column16: Cristian Guzman grounds into double play, second baseman Alexi Casilla to shortstop J.   Hardy to first baseman Michael Cuddyer.    Taylor Teagarden out at 2nd.
Taylor Teagarden grounds into a force out, shortstop J.   Hardy to second baseman Alexi Casilla.    Mitch Moreland to 3rd.    Jeff Francoeur out at 2nd.    Taylor Teagarden to 1st.
Jeff Francoeur singles on a ground ball to center fielder Denard Span.    Mitch Moreland to 2nd.
Ian Kinsler homers (7) on a fly ball to left field.
